>euan</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Moonstone meld extremely good knowledge of employment law with excellent client care skills.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Legal 500</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">What stands out most is the strong sense of togetherness and feeling valued. Combined with outstanding progression opportunities, makes it an ideal place to build a career.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Legal500</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Euan Lawrence was outstanding. His empathy and communication skills provide a real sense of client care. He uses his experience to advise from a position of authority, as well as being caringly clear about the relative chances of success in given scenarios.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Legal 500</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was dealt with sensitively and I felt lik